snippet.title: Secession Studios
snippet.description: Secession Studios is an L.A based music studio created by composer Greg Dombrowski.  Secession has provided music for countless movie trailers such as The Green Knight, Dunkirk, War for the Planet of the Apes, etc.  Powerful emotions, dramatic themes, and epic orchestra are only a taste of this relentless body of work.  www.SecessionStudios.com
